ICUFN 2019

The TTL is mandatory to avoid broadcast storm in flooding. In addition, if a node receives the same packet that has been forwarded by the node, the packet is discarded to prevent loop. Nevertheless, flooding is not always efficient as multi-hop forwarding method because so many duplicated packets are forwarded by short-distance neighbors.

